text: "Into the Void" is a 1971 song by heavy metal band Black Sabbath and is the final track from their third studio album Master of Reality. It has a mix of heavy metal and doom metal thrown into it. It was covered by Soundgarden and Kyuss in 1996. ==References== Category:1971 songs Category:Black Sabbath songs Category:Soundgarden songs Category:Kyuss songs
